title: The Jade Pussycat (1977).avi
description:
IMDB review.............

Practically overflowing with charisma, John C Holmes seems apt at sticking his personality in all the right places. This Holmes classic finds Johnny Wadd on the trail of A fabled Jade Pussycat, which is very valuable and in danger of coming into the possesion of an evil gangster. It's up to Johnny and his 13 inch partner to fight and charm his way through femme fatals, sleazy lowlives, and coming face to face with the jade pussycat before it's to late. If John Holmes credibility as an actor, and not just a phallic symbol were ever doubted, The Jade Pussycat, singlehandedly dispells any such thoughts. One of the big man's best.
